data.description: Ranch style home in sunny Rio Dell. This home features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath and half bath in the master bedroom. Large open living area that adjoins the dining room, step-saving kitchen, and laundry room. Nice size fully fenced yard with shed and attached car garage that provides room for extra storge.
